"{\"uid\": \"www.independent.ie.-world-news-africa-mary-robinson-events-like-brexit-distracting-as-millions-of-ethiopians-suffer-the\", \"text\": \"United Nations envoy Mary Robinson has accused the international community of being distracted and preoccupied by events like Brexit as millions of Ethiopians suffer the worst drought in half a century.  The former president of Ireland hit out after being briefed on the devastating impacts of the El Nino weather pattern and climate change which has seen rains and harvests fail over the last year.\"}"